# Build artifacts (anchored to repo root only — don't accidentally
# match the cmd/zapgen package directory).
/zapgen
# The zapgen binary built in-place in its package dir (`go build` with no
# -o lands here); a compiled artifact, never source.
/cmd/zapgen/zapgen
# The agents example binary built in-place at the repo root (go build
# ./examples/agents with no -o lands here); a compiled artifact.
/agents
*.test
*.out

